      public int getColumnDisplaySize(int column) throws SQLException
      Gets a columns display size

      Since RDF imposes no maximum on the size of a term this may be arbitrarily large hence Integer.MAX_VALUE is returned, users should not rely on this method to give them accurate information for UI usage.
